<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Has studied economy and political sciences as well as at the Institut des Hautes Etudes Cinematographique (IDHEC) in Paris, France. Worked as an assistant director with <a href="/name/nm0001501?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">Louis Malle</a>, <a href="/name/nm0578483?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">Jean-Pierre Melville</a> and <a href="/name/nm0720297?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">Alain Resnais</a>. Founded his own production company Bioskop Film together with <a href="/name/nm0369240?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk4">Reinhard Hauff</a> and <a href="/name/nm0432723?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk5">Eberhard Junkersdorf</a> in 1973. Has directed ...            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0772522/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
